Serializable, org.apache.ojb.broker.PersistenceBrokerAware, EndowmentAccountingLine, org.kuali.rice.kns.bo.BusinessObject, org.kuali.rice.kns.bo.PersistableBusinessObject
public class SourceEndowmentAccountingLine
extends EndowmentAccountingLineBase

Represents the "source" grouping of accounting lines in a given Endowment Transfer of Funds document. Its counterpart is the TargetEndowmentAccountingLine class. Both objects' data is stored in the DB in a single table named "ENDOW_ACCT_LINES_T."
